SUMMARY:Quagmire in Iran: Lunch with Political Science Faculty
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Political Science']\\nCategory: Meeting\\nPleas
 e join Jason Hartwig and the Political Science Department this Monday
 \, April 6th\, for another Lunch with Faculty discussion on the conflic
 t in Iran.   Professor Hartwig is an expert on the unintended consequen
 ces of military intervention and a US army veteran who led tank and scout 
 platoons during the troop surges in Iraq and Afghanistan. We will discuss 
 his experiences during those wars as well as the political and strategic c
 hallenges facing leaders wanting to extricate the US from protracted confl
 icts in far-off lands.  Students\, faculty and staff from across the Col
 lege are welcome to join. Pizza and drinks will be served. \\nDetails: ht
 tps://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D138
 5489352
LOCATION:Old Science Hall Room 303-Classroom
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1385489352
CATEGORIES:Meeting
END:VEVENT
