SUMMARY:Martin Hall Sustainability Open House
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Sustainability']\\nCategory: Conference\\nIn pa
 rtnership with Green Building United\, the Office of Sustainability and Su
 stainable Facilities Operations and Capital Planning is hosting a full day
  of events celebrating the sustainable design of Martin Hall\, the Dining 
 and Community Commons\, and the College’s ambitious To Zero By Thirty-Fi
 ve energy plan. All events are free and open to the public\, with pre-regi
 stration required for most sessions. Events will take place throughout the
  day on Thursday\, April 16. Register for free and build your agenda for 
 the day!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3
