SUMMARY:Group Circuit Training with Chris
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Recreation & Wellness']\\nCategory: Recreation-
 General\\nDo you struggle to figure out which workout to do at the gym\, o
 r do you need some extra motivation? If so\, this class is for you. Receiv
