SUMMARY:SwatTank Pitch Competition
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Center for Innovation and Leadership']\\nCatego
 ry: Lecture/Panel Discussion\\nSwatTank is an idea competition\, guiding s
 tudents through the process of conceptualization to pitch. Students start 
 with a rough idea or product and develop it with workshops\, mentorship\, 
 and collaboration. The students with the most well-developed ideas are inv
 ited to pitch their product to a panel of judges in the SwatTank finals. T
 eams are assessed on overall business idea\, creativity\, and quality of t
 heir pitch and are rewarded through cash prizes.\\nDetails: https://swatce
 ntral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1344125709
LOCATION:Science Center Room 101- Chang Hou Hall Tiered Classroom\, Science
