  and subject matter expertise to our community. Voices Matter is a signatu
 re program under the leadership of the Intercultural Center that aims to p
 rovide the college and surrounding community with world-class speakers and
  lectures that specialize in enhancing global stewardship\, humanity\, and
  cultural competency. They will be formatted in a keynote lecture style or
  a moderated Q&A program.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?t
