  Center\, Chang Hou Hall Room 101500 College AveSwarthmore\, PA 19081 Join
  fellow Philadelphia-area alumni for a special on-campus event. 7 p.m. | D
 oors Open7:30 p.m. | Lecture Begins Hear from Robert Putnam ’63\, H’90
 \, widely regarded as the world's most influential living social scientist
