 d most recent book. Space is limited. RSVPs will be accepted until Friday\
 , April 17\, or until the event reaches capacity\, whichever comes first. 
 Be sure to join us for an unforgettable\, thought-provoking evening. RSVP 
 here!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Dev
 ent%26eventid%3D1385489004
