SUMMARY:DRAGMORE
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['GSC'\, 'Be Well']\\nCategory: Student Activity 
 (no alcohol)\\nStep into DRAGMORE - a kaleidoscope of fabulousness where e
 very sequin shimmers with stories untold and every strut is a declaration 
 of fierce empowerment. Our drag show isn't just a spectacle\; it's a journ
 ey into a world where glitter reigns supreme and authenticity knows no bou
 nds. Get ready to be dazzled as performers take the stage\, transforming i
 nto larger-than-life personas with a wink\, a nod\, and a whole lot of att
 itude. From jaw-dropping lip-syncs to gravity-defying dance moves\, each a
 ct is a celebration of self-expression and uninhibited creativity. As the 
 lights dim and the music pulses through your veins\, prepare to be swept a
 way on a whirlwind of glamour\, humor\, and unapologetic fabulousness. Whe
 ther you're a seasoned drag aficionado or a first-time reveler\, our show 
 promises an unforgettable evening of laughter\, love\, and pure\, unadulte
 rated fun. So grab your glitter\, unleash your inner diva\, and join us fo
 r a night where anything is possible—and everyone is a star.\\nDetails: 
 https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1
 373113776
LOCATION:Clothier Room TIC-Upper Tarble - Multi Purpose Room
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1373113776
CATEGORIES:Student Activity (no alcohol)
END:VEVENT
