 r)\, erhu (bowed fiddle)\, pipa (plucked lute)\, yangqin (hammered dulcime
 r)\, dizi (flute)\, and percussion.  The concert program can be found her
 e. This performance will be streamed live.  Swarthmore College encourages
  persons with disabilities to participate in its programs and activities. 
